*PStrip - procedural version of the Strip function.
See also Strip, Mop, Purge
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------}
procedure TStringManager.PStrip(var s: String; c : Char = ' '; DoUpcase : Boolean = False);
var   i : Integer;
  aStop : Integer;
